values:
yes... here i sit. alone in the dark crying over an ex boyfriend. who turned out to be a real jerk, and doesn't give a shit less about me anymore.

and knowing this. here i sit. i sit and cry over what was and what isn't. i hate it that i miss him. i miss everything about him. i miss him so bad i'd give almost anything just to fight with him one more time. just to hear his voice. but he doesn't care about me. not any more. and i'm sitting here wondering if he's better off. i know my friends, out of the kindness of their hearts and love for me, would say i deserve so much better and that he's stupid for letting me go. but is that the truth? or is it just a sugar coated version of what's really there? i know that in the end we simply weren't meant to be... i just wish it hurt less. 

and this event has drained me so much, and made me bitter. i don't know how, when, or if i can ever trust my heart with another male. because no matter what, the story ends the same. my heart and emotions ripped to shreds. how i hate it. trust can be such an aweful thing. it's not that i never want to be in love again.. or never have another boyfriend, but the whole time i'm just going to be waiting for the end. and if all you have to look forward to is your ultimate destination, can you enjoy the ride? 

this is what i get for staying up till 6 in the morning. sick and walking down a not so bright memory lane. alas... i have stopped crying. that's something.

I wish i could forget. forget everything about the last year. i don't really hurt anymore. but the fact that i've become so numb makes me sad. i can't feel anything for anyone but him. every song i hear makes me think of him. he's always on my mind. it doesn't hurt. not really. i just miss him a lot. why is this? he did me so wrong... he won't even talk to me now... and i didn't even do anything wrong. so why do i miss him... why is that i'd give anything for him to be mine one more time... just for a day... an hour... a minute... who cares? just one more anything! i'd give anything to tell him that i love him right this second. that i miss him and i don't want things to end this way. i'd do anything to hold him and kiss him one last time... but he's gone. he's with someone else (i'm only like 75% sure of that one). he obviously doesn't care anymore... or he'd be here now... he's over me and i'm stuck here in a ghost world full of memories of him, of us. i can't be sure of my emotions anymore. all i feel is hurt... when i can feel at all. this'll get better.. i know it will.

this is something little...  

I'm not broken.
Trust me, I'm just fine.
Because I know that
God heals all wounds in time.
You may see me bend,
But you'll rarely see me break.
My strength is one thing
That I don't have to fake.

lol i haven't wrote on here in a long time.. it seems like. i don't mean to not update.. but you know how it is. life happens and the days go by faster than they used to. and then you step back and it's like "What the hell happened to Monday?" lol. i dunno. that's just how i feel sometimes. like i'm rushing so much sometimes i meet myself in between things and i'm like "Hi there. Haven't seen you in a while. How ya been?" "Oh ya know. Busy." lol i'm such an idiot. OMG. ya know that feeling you get when you see something.. like you've seen it before, but can't for the life of you think when.. starts with a d.. french word.. dunno how to spell it.. anyway! the other day i was waiting in the hall to ask Cody if i could borrow his MP3.. and omg i felt it. i was standing there and.. it was something.. like a dream. it was like time stopped for a second. i swear to you.. omg it was sooooo strange. gawd. there was just something in the way we were standing in the hall i guess. and i swear to you.. for what seemed like a long time.. time stood still. i swear it. omg i can't get over it. *shivers*. and then last night i had the DUMBEST.. (that's a word..) dream about him EVER! i guess i was talking to him on the phone.. but i could see him? and then i hung up and tried to take a bath.. but the floor filled up with water instead of the tub? and the water didn't leave the bathroom.. it was way weird. and i guess after a second i gave up and went back in the living room and mom was like "i invited Cody to church in the morning.. he'll be here in a minute so get ready". and the clock said 1 am.. and i was like "now?" and she's like "yea.. duh" O_o what a weirdo. and then i had to take him somewhere.. at 1 in the morning!!! gosh! and yea.. that was it. lol. newho. i guess this is a long enough update for now. SEE YA *peace love and rock* buh-bye

dad made me so mad today. he just yells at me for no damn reason other than he's being an asshole at the moment. i mean really. k here's what happened. this chick calls (telemarketer) and is like foreign okay. and mom like tells her that she's too busy to talk and that she needs to call back at a different time. and like 5 seconds after my mom hangs up.. the chick calls back! i didn't know that mom had said that.. so i answer the phone, thinking dad was being a jerk and hung up on her (he was who she asked for). so i like tell him that she's on the phone again... AND HE YELLS AT ME! i'm not the idiot who called back.. i was relaying a damn messege! and he yells at me. so i said "i'm sorry i didn't realize what happened" and he yells some more. saying i coped an attitude. i love that. no matter what i say to him.. i'm having an attitude. and i prolly wouldn't have been so upset over it.. except it was in front of my out of state family. and my aunt like gave me a pitty look cause of it. mom felt the need to appologize for him. and i was just like whatever. 30 minutes to an hour later he says he's sorry for hurting my feelings and yelling at me. save it. appologize to our family.. i'm sure it was just as bad for them as it was for me. how embarrassing. it's not the first time he's humiliated me in front of 'company' either. not the worst he's done tho.. by far. *gah* that just makes me mad. i can't ever do anything good enough for him. and i try. i do. if i draw something i think is kewl.. or mom and kelly said was kewl... i like show him. and he's like yea? makes me mad. 
i'm done.

my throat hurts soo bad. i feel terrible. i don't want to be sick. it makes me mad. my family is full of nasty tasting remedies and i'm going to have to try all of them until i'm well.. GAH! i didn't really start feeling bad until about 11:30 last night though. i dunno. 

my mind is all confused. i really don't want to be mad but i find myself there. and then i feel like a hypocrite when i am mad. i think i deserve the right to be mad. but i don't really want to... i want to forget. forget all of it. every last minute. i wish it never happened. and i hate feeling like that. i really do. i feel like an idiot. i am an idiot. i knew. i so did. and i let it happen. i'm tired of trusting people. most of all men. people should come with a warning sign. like "warning: will lie exsessivly and break your heart". yea.. like that. or "warning: shy, feels uncomfortable in social settings.. but i will love you unconditionally" *sigh*.. i bet i could make mine if i wanted. but that's more than i think anyone should really know. stupid probably says it best. yep. i wish i couldn't feel. i'm past the point of feeling hurt.. i just.. don't want to be hurt again. like ever. this sucks.

Some examples of why the human race has probably evolved as far as possible. These are actual instruction labels on consumer goods:

On Sears hairdryer:
Do not use while sleeping.
(Gee, that's the only time I have to work on my hair!)

On a bag of Fritos:
You could be a winner! No purchase necessary. Details inside.
(The shoplifter special!)

On a bar of Dial soap:
Directions: Use like regular soap.
(and that would be how?)

On some Swann frozen dinners:
Serving suggestion: Defrost.
(But it's 'just' a suggestion!)

On Tesco's Tiramisu dessert: (printed on bottom of the box)
Do not turn upside down.
(Too late! you lose!)

On Marks & Spencer Bread Pudding:
Product will be hot after heating.
(Are you sure? Let's experiment.)

On packaging for a Rowenta iron:
Do not iron clothes on body.

Cody and Chantry have joined the NAVY. I have to admit, that I really don't like that little fact. If I had any say, what so ever... they'd be going to college and doing something for a living that wouldn't have a chance for them to get hurt. We're practically in a war for crying out loud! I've put up with too much crap, from the people who live here.. I don't want that for the rest of my life. I dread the last day of skool. I dread walking into the cafetorium for the Senior graduation... because when it ends, that's what I'll be... a Senior. That is so scary to me. How did time pass do fast? I think I'll be leaving now. *peace love and rock* buh-bye
